{"tid":1681104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"掟五星旗落城門河 21歲男子判200小時社服令","createTime":"2019-10-29T08:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T08:27:32.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bea729fa20a1d1c48ae05910d6311ad1e3c7319e","tid":1681104,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:08:21.000Z","msg":"一名21歲男子上月22日在沙田涉嫌踐踏及掟五星旗落城門河，早前承認一項侮辱國旗罪，今日在沙田裁判法院被判200小時社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官表示，考慮到被告認罪，過往沒有定罪紀錄，加上有家人支持及感化報告正面，因此判處服務令。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2287136/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2287136%2F&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg%2FsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=74c454a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2287136/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89297cc936bd94e94d2f7025a84a5e61c928ff29","tid":1681104,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:08:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"cbedc8242659a8f79b18bf780b58cb0f147d86fb","tid":1681104,"uid":270563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a1053835655adaae7ee91287a42b9e1f7f1e8b0","tid":1681104,"uid":100985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7NOjJs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7NOjJs.gif&h=d5f5ef2f